            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "That was very good..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Thank you very much."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x30,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Oh, Cory? It's unusual to meet you at the cafe."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Yes, I had never come here before... I never cared for tea, after all..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "But I'm glad they had more than just tea to drink."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "I try my best to prepare for any guest to have an enjoyable time here."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x34,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Just as I'd expect. But why did you decide to come here today?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x1b,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "I came to deliver an order to Mr. Horst, and he treated me as thanks..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x3d,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "I didn't expect that you don't care for tea, though."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "But everything here was delicious. I'll come back."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x3e,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "See you again..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x42,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Thank you for visiting."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Cory seemed really happy."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x17,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Visiting a shop for the first time can make you nervous. She must simply feel relieved."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xd,
            "name_id": 0xd,
            "extra_id": 0x18,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "Sophie, feel free to relax and take your time here too."
        }
    ]
